RT-Extension-SpawnLinkedTicket version 0.0.1

How to install:

1. perl Makefile.PL
2. make
3. make install (may need root permissions)
4. Edit your /opt/rt3/etc/RT_SiteConfig.pm 
    Set(@Plugins, qw(RT::Extension::SpawnLinkedTicket));
5. rm -rf /opt/rt3/var/mason_data/obj
6. Restart your webserver

